{"type":null,"faqId":45206,"title":"新手机充电有哪些注意事项？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.19861111in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0791667in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>尽量使用原装电池、充电器。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>不要等到低电量状态再为电池充电，尽量随用随充，以延长电池的使用寿命。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>电池充满后，请及时断开充电器，否则可能会损伤电池和充电器的寿命。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":8,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"706","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442451578000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":336,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"新手机,充电,注意","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}